<ab facs="#facs_469_r1l5"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / . vnd ſie darvmb beſant / vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
