<ab facs="#facs_469_line_1576407438474_1806">Nu 
<add><ab facs="#facs_469_line_1576407526597_1855"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir ſie <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_469_line_1576407531865_1860">edel cʒü dienſt vnd </ab><ab facs="#facs_469_line_1576407535995_1865">gevallnüʒʒ als pald </ab><ab facs="#facs_469_line_1576407541393_1870">Jr vns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſchrıbt </ab><ab facs="#facs_469_line_1576407545617_1875"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ladung </ab><ab facs="#facs_469_line_1576407549856_1880">geweıſet / vnd </ab></add> <expan>bıtt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
