<add><ab facs="#facs_469_r1l11">durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> gut ſein vnd gnedıklıch <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> laſſen wöllet / </ab>
